# shadcn/ui

- Add components with `npx shadcn@latest add <name>` only.
- Files must live under `src/components/ui/`.
- Minimize edits to generated files; prefer CVA variants or wrappers in `features/`.
- Do not use shadcn Card as hero or primary brand layout.
- Theme through `src/styles/globals.css` token bridge.
